spellathon_solver
=================
A simple shell script for solving the daily spellathon puzzle. Uses the in-built dictionary (/usr/share/dict/words) present in every linux system.

How to use
==========
The script is invoked as :
spellathon <The central letter (or the key letter)> <all the letters including the central one>

e.g. If the puzzle is : rctice cith A in the centre
The command line should be:

$ ./spellathon k rcticek
crick
cricket
kite
rick
tick
ticker
tike
trek
trick
trike
	Total : 10
